data.description: Nestled in the midst of majestic pine trees you will find this completely remodeled cream puff. Peaceful setting with a 4 bedroom, 2 bath home on 2.34 acres just minutes from Baron Fork creek. You will fall in love with the Primary suite and bath  that was added on. Stunning bamboo flooring and cedar cabinets in the kitchen. Granite counters, farm style apron kitchen sink.  ADT alarm system has 4 cameras and a glass breaking sensor. Fiber optics for the convenience of working from home. Well water is the best and past the VA inspections. Septic tank was pumped in 2021, New roof. Enjoy the abundance of deer from the front room.  Come HOME to Tahlequah!
